<i>♪ There is nothing</i>
<i>can console me ♪</i>

850
01:00:59.820 --> 01:01:03.460
<i>♪ But my jolly sailor bold ♪</i>

851
01:01:21.700 --> 01:01:23.740
Lord save me.

852
01:01:27.300 --> 01:01:30.260
Man, look. Look there.
[gasps]

853
01:01:30.340 --> 01:01:32.340
[grunts]
You'll scare her off!

854
01:01:32.420 --> 01:01:34.380
Aye, and good riddance!

855
01:01:38.860 --> 01:01:40.580
Can you talk?

856
01:01:42.940 --> 01:01:44.220
Yes.

857
01:01:51.740 --> 01:01:53.060
You're beautiful.

858
01:01:54.540 --> 01:01:58.100
Are you the one who sings?
[Scrum] Aye.

859
01:02:00.860 --> 01:02:03.460
Are you my jolly sailor bold?

860
01:02:03.900 --> 01:02:05.140
[chuckles]

861
01:02:05.540 --> 01:02:08.300
Aye, that I be.
Scrum, comport yourself!

862
01:02:08.420 --> 01:02:11.780
Boys! There ain't much
been given to me

863
01:02:11.860 --> 01:02:14.180
in my brief, miserable life,
there's the truth in it.

864
01:02:14.260 --> 01:02:15.780
But, by God,
I'll have it said

865
01:02:15.860 --> 01:02:19.140
that Scrum had himself a kiss
from a proper mermaid!

866
01:02:19.220 --> 01:02:21.100
[grunts]

867
01:02:21.180 --> 01:02:24.500
<i>[mermaid] ♪ My heart</i>
<i>is pierced by Cupid ♪</i>

868
